name: Application of securities law
text: §417E‑11    [Section effective July 1, 2008.  For section effective until June 30, 2008, see above.]  All of the provisions of chapter 485A that are not in conflict with this chapter shall apply to any take-over offer involving a target company in this State. [L 1985, c 32, pt of §2; am L 2006, c 229, §12]
